track_notes: Easy walk to this summit in winter you must get snowshoes to have the 3 points bonus!
Family walk, best to have the dinner at the restaurant le Christiana after the walk!in winter be carefull with the skiing men. walk on the side
This track is the fastest if you can run while climbing!

Nice path to the summit, slope is hard, get some water in summertime and watch out for the wind.
Of course plenty room for antenna.
track_title: Not the shorter but the nicer
